fig:.playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-48-36-758Z.yml", "type": "config", "name": "", "filePath": ".playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-48-36-758Z.yml", "summary": "Playwright 页面快照 (2026-05-25)", "tags": []}, {"id": "config:.playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-48-44-649Z.yml", "type": "config", "name": "", "filePath": ".playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-48-44-649Z.yml", "summary": "Playwright 页面快照 (2026-05-25)", "tags": []}, {"id": "config:.playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-48-53-046Z.yml", "type": "config", "name": "", "filePath": ".playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-48-53-046Z.yml", "summary": "Playwright 页面快照 (2026-05-25)", "tags": []}, {"id": "config:.playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-49-00-386Z.yml", "type": "config", "name": "", "filePath": ".playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-49-00-386Z.yml", "summary": "Playwright 页面快照 (2026-05-25)", "tags": []}, {"id": "config:.playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-49-11-907Z.yml", "type": "config", "name": "", "filePath": ".playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T01-49-11-907Z.yml", "summary": "Playwright 页面快照 (2026-05-25)", "tags": []}, {"id": "config:.playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T02-59-29-548Z.yml", "type": "config", "name": "", "filePath": ".playwright-mcp/page-2026-05-25T02-59-29-548Z.yml", "summary": "Playwright 页面快照 (2026-05-25)", "tags": []}, {"id": "file:mind-land-server/README.md", "type": "file", "name": "README.md", "filePath": "mind-land-server/README.md", "summary": "mind-land-server 后端服务的项目文档，概述了 Go + Gin + GORM + SQLite 技术栈、快速启动命令、项目目录结构（main.go、slipbox/、todo/ 子包）、完整的 SlipBox 和 ToDo API 路由表、生产部署方式（编译为单一二进制并内嵌前端静态文件）以及 MIT 协议信息。", "tags": ["documentation", "readme", "backend", "go", "api-reference"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-server/go.mod", "type": "file", "name": "go.mod", "filePath": "mind-land-server/go.mod", "summary": "Go 模块定义文件，模块名为 mind-land-server，使用 Go 1.26.2。声明了五个直接依赖：gin-gonic/gin（HTTP 路由）、gin-contrib/cors（跨域中间件）、glebarez/sqlite（纯 Go SQLite 驱动）、gorm.io/gorm（ORM 框架）、golang.org/x/net（网络库），以及约 30 个间接依赖。", "tags": ["go-module", "dependency", "config", "backend"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-server/go.sum", "type": "file", "name": "go.sum", "filePath": "mind-land-server/go.sum", "summary": "Go 依赖锁文件，记录了 go.mod 中所有直接和间接依赖的模块版本哈希值，用于确保可重复构建。包含 gin、gorm、sqlite、sonic、quic-go 等库的校验和。", "tags": ["go-module", "checksum", "lock-file", "config"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-server/package.json", "type": "file", "name": "package.json", "filePath": "mind-land-server/package.json", "summary": "存放在服务器目录的 Node.js 配置文件，声明了 dompurify（HTML 净化库）作为运行时依赖，以及 @types/dompurify 作为类型定义开发依赖，用于在服务端进行 HTML 消毒处理。", "tags": ["config", "npm", "dompurify", "sanitization"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-web/index.html", "type": "file", "name": "index.html", "filePath": "mind-land-web/index.html", "summary": "前端应用的 HTML 入口文件，Vite 开发服务器托管的页面。包含 meta 标签设置（字符集、视口、主题色 #0A0A0F、描述），引入 favicon 和 PWA manifest.json，通过 `<script type=\"module\" src=\"/src/index.tsx\">` 挂载 React 应用到 `#root` 节点。备注移除 Google Fonts 以规避 GFW 封锁。", "tags": ["html", "entry-point", "vite", "pwa"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-web/package.json", "type": "file", "name": "package.json", "filePath": "mind-land-web/package.json", "summary": "前端项目的 npm 配置清单。定义了三个脚本（dev 启动 Vite、build 执行双重 TypeScript 检查后构建、preview 预览产物）。运行时依赖包括 React 19、Redux Toolkit、TipTap 编辑器全家桶、axios、zustand、lucide-react 图标、dayjs 日期库等。开发依赖包括 Vite 6、Tailwind CSS 4、TypeScript 5.7、Vite React 插件和 @tailwindcss/vite。", "tags": ["npm", "config", "dependencies", "scripts", "frontend"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-web/tsconfig.app.json", "type": "file", "name": "tsconfig.app.json", "filePath": "mind-land-web/tsconfig.app.json", "summary": "TypeScript 应用编译配置，针对前端源码（src/ 目录）。目标 ES2020，使用 bundler 模块解析，启用 JSX react-jsx 模式。开启严格模式、未使用变量/参数检查、fallthrough 检查等严格 lint 规则。配置了 `@/*` 路径别名映射到 `./src/*`，使用 composite 项目引用和独立的 tsBuildInfoFile。", "tags": ["typescript", "config", "compiler-options", "path-alias"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-web/tsconfig.json", "type": "file", "name": "tsconfig.json", "filePath": "mind-land-web/tsconfig.json", "summary": "TypeScript 根配置文件，作为项目引用的入口。同样设定 ES2020 目标、bundler 模块解析、strict 模式、react-jsx 等基础选项。定义了 `@/*` 路径别名，通过 include 覆盖 src/ 目录和 vite-env.d.ts 类型声明文件。实际引用 tsconfig.app.json 和 tsconfig.node.json 两个子配置。", "tags": ["typescript", "config", "root-config", "project-references"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-web/tsconfig.node.json", "type": "file", "name": "tsconfig.node.json", "filePath": "mind-land-web/tsconfig.node.json", "summary": "TypeScript Node 环境编译配置，针对 Vite 配置文件（vite.config.ts）。使用 composite 模式、ESNext 模块系统、bundler 模块解析，启用 allowSyntheticDefaultImports 以兼容 CommonJS 模块。", "tags": ["typescript", "config", "node", "vite"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-web/public/index.html", "type": "file", "name": "index.html", "filePath": "mind-land-web/public/index.html", "summary": "生产构建用的 HTML 模板文件，来源于 Create React App 模板工程。使用 `%PUBLIC_URL%` 占位符引用 favicon、apple-touch-icon 和 manifest.json。包含典型的 CRA 模板注释和 `noscript` 回退提示，挂载点为 `#root`。（注意：实际 Vite 构建以根目录 index.html 为准，此文件为遗留模板。）", "tags": ["html", "template", "production", "legacy", "cra"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-web/public/manifest.json", "type": "file", "name": "manifest.json", "filePath": "mind-land-web/public/manifest.json", "summary": "PWA Web App Manifest 配置文件，继承自 Create React App 模板。定义应用名称为「Create React App Sample」，包含三种尺寸图标（favicon、192x192、512x512），设置 start_url 为根路径、display 为 standalone（独立窗口模式）、theme_color 为 #000000、background_color 为 #ffffff。", "tags": ["pwa", "manifest", "config", "icons", "progressive-web-app"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-web/public/robots.txt", "type": "file", "name": "robots.txt", "filePath": "mind-land-web/public/robots.txt", "summary": "搜索引擎爬虫配置文件。允许所有 User-agent 抓取整个网站（Disallow 为空），未设置 Sitemap 路径。引用 robots.txt 标准协议文档链接。", "tags": ["seo", "robots", "crawler", "config"]}, {"id": "file:.claude/memory/session-log.md", "type": "file", "name": "session-log.md", "filePath": ".claude/memory/session-log.md", "summary": "Claude AI 助手的会话活动日志文件（Markdown 格式），记录开发过程中按会话组织的作业日志。内容以日文和中文混合书写，指示重要决策应迁移至 decisions.md、可重用解法应迁移至 patterns.md 文件。", "tags": ["文档", "Markdown", "会话日志", "Claude"]}, {"id": "file:.claude/sessions/.last_inbox_check", "type": "file", "name": ".last_inbox_check", "filePath": ".claude/sessions/.last_inbox_check", "summary": "存储收件箱(inbox)最后检查时间戳的文件，仅包含一个 Unix 时间戳数字（1779024386），用于记录上次检查收件箱的时间点。", "tags": ["时间戳", "元数据", "Claude"]}, {"id": "file:.claude/settings.local.json", "type": "file", "name": "settings.local.json", "filePath": ".claude/settings.local.json", "summary": "Claude Code 的本地设置文件（JSON 格式），配置了权限白名单（allow 列表），包含 grep、curl、git、rm、python3、pnpm、npx tsc、node、env 等命令的执行权限，以及文件读取路径白名单。", "tags": ["配置文件", "JSON", "权限设置", "Claude"]}, {"id": "file:.understand-anything/.understandignore", "type": "file", "name": ".understandignore", "filePath": ".understand-anything/.understandignore", "summary": "understand-anything 代码分析工具的忽略规则配置文件，语法类似 .gitignore。定义需排除的分析文件模式，包括测试文件（*.test.*、*.spec.*）和快照文件（*.snap）。默认内置排除 node_modules/、.git/、dist/、build/ 等目录。", "tags": ["配置文件", "忽略规则", "代码分析"]}, {"id": "file:.understand-anything/config.json", "type": "file", "name": "config.json", "filePath": ".understand-anything/config.json", "summary": "understand-anything 分析工具的全局配置文件，设置输出语言为中文（{\"outputLanguage\": \"zh\"}），指导所有分析摘要使用中文生成。", "tags": ["配置文件", "JSON", "代码分析"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-server/.claude/sessions/.last_inbox_check", "type": "file", "name": ".last_inbox_check", "filePath": "mind-land-server/.claude/sessions/.last_inbox_check", "summary": "mind-land-server 子项目的收件箱最后检查时间戳文件，内容为 Unix 时间戳 1779022080。", "tags": ["时间戳", "元数据", "Claude"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-server/.claude/state/breezing-timeline.jsonl", "type": "file", "name": "breezing-timeline.jsonl", "filePath": "mind-land-server/.claude/state/breezing-timeline.jsonl", "summary": "mind-land-server 的 Claude 状态时间线日志（JSONL 格式），记录了一次任务完成事件：Phase 1 后端错误修复，包含 8 个子任务（GORM 事务错误修复、JSON 序列化错误修复、PatchItem 零值处理等），时间戳为 2026-05-17T12:47:25Z。", "tags": ["时间线", "JSONL", "Claude状态", "任务记录"]}, {"id": "file:mind-land-server/.claude/state/changed